                                Aim
                            </td>
                            
                        </tr>
                    </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p class = 'text-center'>
                Powered by <a href="http://gamejs.org">GameJs</a> and <a href='http://opengameart.org/'>Open game art</a>, Created by <a href='https://github.com/fm2munsh'>Farhan Munshi</a>
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>